Dirt, Wood & Sapling

	As you woke up, you find a chest next to you. Open up and look inside it, what you could find was a piece of dirt, a sapling, some bottles of fertilizer, as well as a trustly pickaxe. 

	While you gathering those items from the chest, you really got no idea about "Why am I here?" nor "Who am I, anyway?". And as you deeply thinking into it, nothing but painful is what you feel.

WOOD!

	Now you have a pickaxe. You decided to break out the room and see what happened outside.
	As soon as you breach the wall, you've seen nothing in your sight, Not Even A Single Block.

	Little time took you to realize that the world is no longer in exists. And you... are the only one left among this broken realm....

	Though still shocked by the fact, you spared a look at the sapling in your hands. Flashing memory showed you a mysterious human being...


... planting a sapling on a block of dirt?
